import React from 'react' const CourseScorecard = (props) => { let par_holes = props.par_holes let outScore = 0; for(let i = 0; i < 9; i++){ outScore += par_holes[i]; } let inScore = 0; for(let i = 9; i < par_holes.length; i++){ inScore += par_holes[i]; } return (
Hole 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 Out 10 11 12 13 14 15 16 17 18 In Total
) } export default CourseScorecard
